ZH: 我一直缺乏胆量，从不敢做任何冒险的事情。
EN: I have always lacked courage and never dare to do anything risky.

ZH: 他展示出了巨大的胆量，在困境中保持冷静。
EN: He showed immense courage, staying calm in a difficult situation.

ZH: 她的胆量令人钦佩，从不怕面对挑战。
EN: Her courage is admirable; she is never afraid to face challenges.

ZH: 他是个胆小鬼，缺乏胆量面对任何危险。
EN: He is a coward and lacks the courage to face any danger.

