EN: It takes some courage to speak in public.

ZH: 他的胆量不错，勇于尝试新事物。
EN: His courage is commendable; he is willing to try new things.

ZH: 他凭借坚定的胆量克服了许多困难。
EN: He overcame many difficulties with his resolute courage.

